Package edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.application

Class Application

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.application.Application
public class Application extends Object
The Application class represents a job application with various states and attributes such as an ID, summary, reviewer, paperwork status, and notes.
Author:
Priyanshu Dongre

    • Application

      public Application(int id, String state, String appType, String summary, String reviewer, boolean confirmed, String resolution, ArrayList<String> notes)
      Overloaded constructor for an existing Application.
      Parameters:
      id - The application ID.
      state - The current state of the application.
      appType - The type of application (as a String).
      summary - A summary of the application.
      reviewer - The name of the reviewer.
      confirmed - Whether the application is confirmed.
      resolution - The resolution of the application.
      notes - A list of notes related to the application.
